Introduction

Lee Je No is a member of the South Korean boy group NCT and is the lead dancer, lead rapper, and visual of its sub-unit NCT Dream. Aside from singing and dancing, Jeno is also good at playing the guitar and even acting. In 2018, along with Jaemin, Jeno appeared in the web drama A-Teen.

On August 24, 2016, Jeno debuted in NCT Dream, the third sub-unit of NCT.
